      <title>乌克兰盟友开始考虑如何实现停火</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-17/ukraine-russia-ceasefire-kyiv-s-allies-start-to-look-at-how-it-could-work</link>
      <description><![CDATA[乌克兰的一些盟友开始谈论抵抗俄罗斯入侵的战斗将如何结束，这引发了其他几个西方国家首都的担忧，他们担心这些努力可能导致基辅被迫过早停火。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-17/ukraine-russia-ceasefire-kyiv-s-allies-start-to-look-at-how-it-could-work</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 17 Sep 2024 12:21:08 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>斯洛伐克罢免反对党领袖，剥夺其议会重要职位</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-17/slovakia-ousts-opposition-leader-from-key-parliament-job</link>
      <description><![CDATA[斯洛伐克执政联盟将反对党领袖从议会副议长职位上撤职，此举引发外界指责，认为这是对总理罗伯特·菲科主要批评者的报复。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-17/slovakia-ousts-opposition-leader-from-key-parliament-job</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 17 Sep 2024 12:13:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧盟将在 LGBTQ 新战略中禁止扭转疗法</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-17/eu-to-pursue-ban-on-conversion-therapy-in-new-lgbtq-strategy</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧盟首次承诺禁止转化疗法，这是欧盟委员会主席乌尔苏拉·冯德莱恩计划在第二任期内推行的一项新的 LGBTQ 平等战略的一部分。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-17/eu-to-pursue-ban-on-conversion-therapy-in-new-lgbtq-strategy</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 17 Sep 2024 12:03:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>意大利承诺预算赤字低于 3%，2021 年有望实现巨额收入</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-17/italy-vows-deficit-below-3-in-budget-reaping-windfall-from-2021</link>
      <description><![CDATA[意大利总理乔治亚·梅洛尼 (Giorgia Meloni) 领导的执政联盟承诺到 2026 年将意大利的预算赤字恢复到欧盟规定的限额以下，此举可能受到疫情期间数据修正的推动。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-17/italy-vows-deficit-below-3-in-budget-reaping-windfall-from-2021</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 17 Sep 2024 11:51:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>马斯克向纽约竞选投入资金，这对共和党众议院胜利至关重要</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-17/musk-pours-money-into-new-york-races-critical-to-house-gop-win</link>
      <description><![CDATA[埃隆·马斯克的超级政治行动委员会正在向全国各地战场地区的共和党候选人提供 210 万美元，这可能有助于这位世界首富在国会建立盟友阵容。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-17/musk-pours-money-into-new-york-races-critical-to-house-gop-win</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 17 Sep 2024 11:46:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美联储准备降息之际，巴西央行行长立场鹰派</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-17/brazil-braces-for-hawkish-central-bank-chief-just-as-fed-readies-rate-cuts</link>
      <description><![CDATA[巴西央行新权力掮客加布里埃尔·加利波罗 (Gabriel Galipolo) 在过去几周内彻底转型为反通胀斗士。加利波罗被任命为央行行长，此举颠覆了拉丁美洲最大经济体的货币政策前景。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-17/brazil-braces-for-hawkish-central-bank-chief-just-as-fed-readies-rate-cuts</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 17 Sep 2024 11:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国誓言克服邻避主义，实现快速能源转型</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-17/uk-vows-to-face-down-nimbyism-to-deliver-rapid-energy-shift</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国能源大臣周二表示，英国不会让邻避主义阻碍 2030 年实现电网脱碳所需的大规模清洁能源建设。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-17/uk-vows-to-face-down-nimbyism-to-deliver-rapid-energy-shift</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 17 Sep 2024 11:29:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>朝鲜最新核计划引发担忧，称其可能向外运输核弹用铀</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-17/north-korea-s-latest-nuclear-work-sparks-fears-it-may-ship-uranium-for-bombs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[有关朝鲜核弹研制活动的新细节引发了人们的担忧，人们担心朝鲜最高领导人金正恩可能向从事非法武器计划的国家提供武器。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-17/north-korea-s-latest-nuclear-work-sparks-fears-it-may-ship-uranium-for-bombs</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 17 Sep 2024 11:23:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>马里军队挫败针对首都军事训练学校的袭击</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-17/mali-army-says-it-thwarted-attack-on-military-training-camp</link>
      <description><![CDATA[马里军队挫败了对首都巴马科军事训练营的袭击，不明身份的袭击者袭击了该市多个目标。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-17/mali-army-says-it-thwarted-attack-on-military-training-camp</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 17 Sep 2024 09:14:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>德国保守党人梅尔茨将挑战舒尔茨担任总理</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-17/german-cdu-leader-merz-seals-conservative-chancellor-candidacy</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德国基督教民主联盟主席弗里德里希·梅尔茨获得保守党候选人资格，挑战奥拉夫·朔尔茨出任总理，在欧洲最大经济体下届大选前一年多的时间里，他击败了众多竞争对手。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-17/german-cdu-leader-merz-seals-conservative-chancellor-candidacy</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 17 Sep 2024 07:28:01 GMT</pubDate>
